{
  "title": "Mild Garlicky Brazilian Pak Koi Skewers",
  "description": "A kid-friendly Brazilian dish featuring garlicky baby pak koi in a glassy-jelly sauce, made with lardons-render for added flavor.",
  "cuisine": "Brazilian",
  "diet": [
